	)
	(text "RS-485 bias (R4/R5): fitted as DNP footprints, insurance only.\nTHVD1429 has integrated open/short/idle failsafe, so the idle bus\nis already defined and no external bias is normally needed.\nBias belongs at ONE point on the bus - the master is that point,\nso if the bench ever disagrees, populate here and nowhere else.\n390R pair = approx. 236mV across the 60R terminated bus at 3.3V."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 14.224 122.936 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(color 124 0 0 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "40989a75-47f0-42dc-b380-c96f02b7d7cc")
	)
	(text "Overall Ground connection is added here to J4, as 2P terminal blocks are \neasy to find and source. We needed a way to connect the ground to the rest\nof the system anyway."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 134.874 121.92 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(color 124 0 0 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "491ff71a-3c89-41ce-b448-17d5fb682677")
	)
